Today, I’m going to recap a&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:34.480
Korean movie released in 2019, called, Innocent&nbsp;
Witness. This story is about a girl with autism,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:00:34.480 --> 00:00:40.320
who is also a key witness to a murder. Because of&nbsp;
her condition, she was unable to testify in court&nbsp;&nbsp;

